cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.MA, cs.AI 

The paper deals with real-time bidding in display advertising, which involves optimization and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is Information Retrieval (cs.IR), followed by Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible categories, given the use of optimization and learning techniques.
